item.title: By: Arthur

item.description: K, I feel your pain. There are an assortment of bands I feel like I should like...but I don't. Sonic Youth is at the top of that list.

item.title: By: Soph
item.dc:creator: Soph
item.description: I'm completely gay for Of Montreal, and how could I resist such an absurd and colourful video! I'll admit it took me a couple of attempts at Hissing Fauna, Are You the Destroyer? to really get into it, but its grown on me! Not so sure about this cover though...
item.content:encoded: I’m completely gay for Of Montreal, and how could I resist such an absurd and colourful video! I’ll admit it took me a couple of attempts at Hissing Fauna, Are You the Destroyer? to really get into it, but its grown on me! Not so sure about this cover though…

item.title: By: K
item.dc:creator: K
item.description: I wish that I could get into Of Montreal. It's not for a lack of effort. I listened to Hissing Fauna a handful of times but it never hooked me. I recognize that Kevin Barnes is pretty much a musical genius, he's just not my cup of tea, I suppose.
item.content:encoded: I wish that I could get into Of Montreal. It’s not for a lack of effort. I listened to Hissing Fauna a handful of times but it never hooked me. I recognize that Kevin Barnes is pretty much a musical genius, he’s just not my cup of tea, I suppose.
